---
model: googleai/gemini-3-pro-preview
input:
  schema:
    company_profile: any
    existing_targets: string
---
Here is the company profile:
{{company_profile}}

Existing targets (DO NOT RETURN THESE):
{{existing_targets}}

Find 20 NEW backlink opportunities for this company:
- 10 targets must be highly relevant, high-quality, niche submission directories or platforms specific to the company's industry.
- 10 targets should be more generic business directories or listings with simpler submission processes (e.g. general startup lists, business aggregators).

Return the result EXACTLY as a JSON array of objects with fields:
- "domain": string (e.g. "producthunt.com")
- "url": string (e.g. "https://producthunt.com/new")
